+--------------------------------------------------------------------+

[0]amigoro writes "Here's an interesting experiment: Copy Google results
pages from four different e-commerce queries. Tell 32 test subjects who
are going to evaluate the results that the results were from four
different search engines: Google, MSN Live Search, Yahoo! and an in-house
engine created for the study. Then [1]see which once they rate as the
best. As it turns out Google and Yahoo! win hands down, proving that even
on the Internet it's all about branding."

